<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tela de Chat</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/chat/chat.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div>
            <h2>Conversas</h2>
            <div style="width: 100%; height: 2px; background-color: #414141;"></div>
        </div>


        <input type="text" placeholder="Buscar" />

    </div>

    <div class="chat-container">
        <div class="chat-header">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="avatar" />
            <span>Usuário 1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="messages">
            <div class="message user">Me envie o arquivo que você tem em mente</div>
            <div class="message other">
                Esse design está maravilhoso! adsdadadsadadaddasdada
                dadsdadadadsadasdasdadadsasdadasdasdasdasdasdasdadadada
            </div>
            <div class="message user">
                Acho que está bom assim, textos espaçados, bl bla bla, dá para escrever bem e o design se ajusta
                facilmente
                aaaaaaaaaaaaaa aaaaaa aaaaaaaaaaaaaaa aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="previewImagemContainer" style="display: none; padding: 10px;">
            <div class="parteSuperiorPreview">
                <button id="fecharPreview"
                    style="margin-top: 10px; background: #333; color: white; border: none; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer;">
                    X
                </button>
            </div>

            <img id="previewImagem" src="" alt="Prévia da imagem" />

        </div>
        <input type="file" id="inputImagemOculto" accept="image/*" style="display: none;" />

        <div id="previewLink" style="display:none; margin-bottom: 5px;"></div>

        <div class="input-area">
            <button class="btnAnexos" id="btnAnexos" style="font-size: 15px;">
                +
            </button>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Digite uma mensagem..." />
            <button id="btnEnviar">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" width="20px" height="20px">
                    <path
                        d="M3.478 2.404a.75.75 0 0 0-.926.941l2.432 7.905H13.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H4.984l-2.432 7.905a.75.75 0 0 0 .926.94 60.519 60.519 0 0 0 18.445-8.986.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.218A60.517 60.517 0 0 0 3.478 2.404Z" />
                </svg>
            </button>

            <div class="menu-anexos" id="menuAnexos">
                <button id="anexarImagem">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M1.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25h16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 22.5 6v12a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 1.5 18V6ZM3 16.06V18c0 .414.336.75.75.75h16.5A.75.75 0 0 0 21 18v-1.94l-2.69-2.689a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-2.12 0l-.88.879.97.97a.75.75 0 1 1-1.06 1.06l-5.16-5.159a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-2.12 0L3 16.061Zm10.125-7.81a1.125 1.125 0 1 1 2.25 0 1.125 1.125 0 0 1-2.25 0Z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>

                    Imagens
                </button>
                <button id="anexarLink">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6"
                        style="transform: rotate(44deg);">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M19.902 4.098a3.75 3.75 0 0 0-5.304 0l-4.5 4.5a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 1.035 6.037.75.75 0 0 1-.646 1.353 5.25 5.25 0 0 1-1.449-8.45l4.5-4.5a5.25 5.25 0 1 1 7.424 7.424l-1.757 1.757a.75.75 0 1 1-1.06-1.06l1.757-1.757a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 0-5.304Zm-7.389 4.267a.75.75 0 0 1 1-.353 5.25 5.25 0 0 1 1.449 8.45l-4.5 4.5a5.25 5.25 0 1 1-7.424-7.424l1.757-1.757a.75.75 0 1 1 1.06 1.06l-1.757 1.757a3.75 3.75 0 1 0 5.304 5.304l4.5-4.5a3.75 3.75 0 0 0-1.035-6.037.75.75 0 0 1-.354-1Z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Link
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="nenhum-contato-selecionado">
            <p>Selecione um contato para iniciar a conversa</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modalLink" style="
    display:none; 
    position: fixed; 
    top: 50%; 
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: #1a1a1a; 
    padding: 25px 30px; 
    border-radius: 12px; 
    z-index: 1000; 
    color: #eee; 
    width: 320px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
">
        <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem;">Inserir Link</h3>
        <input type="text" id="inputLink" placeholder="https://exemplo.com" style="
        width: 100%; 
        padding: 10px 12px; 
        margin-bottom: 20px; 
        border-radius: 6px; 
        border: none; 
        outline: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        background: #2e2e2e; 
        color: #eee;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    " onfocus="this.style.background='#3b3b3b'" onblur="this.style.background='#2e2e2e'">

        <div style="text-align: right;">
            <button id="cancelarLink" style="
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: #aaa;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
        " onmouseover="this.style.color='#fff'; this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.1)'"
                onmouseout="this.style.color='#aaa'; this.style.background='transparent'">Cancelar</button>

            <button id="confirmarLink" style="
            background: #4eaaff;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        " onmouseover="this.style.background='#3b8ae6'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#4eaaff'">Enviar</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
<script type="module" src="/js/chat/chat.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="/js/chat/anexosChat.js"></script>

</html>